    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Account
    Base class for all types of bank accounts.
    Bank
    Manages the main operations of the bank, including users, employees, and loans.
    BankTest
    Tests the main functions of the bank to make sure everything works correctly.
    CheckingAccount
    A type of account that can have transaction fees.
    Loan
    Holds data for a loan request, including the user's income and application status.
    Main
    The main entry point for the Bahaa United Bank application.
    SavingsAccount
    A type of bank account designed for saving money with a strict withdrawal limit.
    Transaction
    Represents a single money movement, like a deposit or withdrawal.
    Transferable
    An interface that defines how money can be moved between different accounts.
